WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.269
Excellent job with some simple,
but important work.

00:00:03.269 --> 00:00:06.192
Your camera is the only window your
player has into your game world.

00:00:06.192 --> 00:00:09.792
So, make sure it presents
the best your world has to offer.

00:00:09.792 --> 00:00:12.876
So, now we have GigaGal,
some platforms to jump on, and

00:00:12.876 --> 00:00:15.078
a camera that can move around the level.

00:00:15.078 --> 00:00:17.334
It's awfully quiet in there though.

00:00:17.334 --> 00:00:20.470
In the next level let's adds
an evil robot buddies to play with.

